#. module: base
#: model:ir.module.module,description:base.module_l10n_au_reports
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"\n"
"Australian Accounting Module\n"
"============================\n"
"\n"
"Taxable Payments Annual Reports (TPAR) for Australia\n"
"\n"
"The Taxable payments annual report (TPAR) allows:\n"
"\n"
"    • Payments made to contractors (or subcontractors) for services, or\n"
"    • Grants paid by government entities to ABN holders\n"
"\n"
"to be reported where required under the Taxable Payments Reporting System "
"(TPRS) and the Taxable Government Grants and Payments reporting measure.\n"
"\n"
"The TPAR is due by 28th August each year.\n"
"\n"
"Penalties may apply if you don’t lodge your TPAR on time.\n"
"\n"
"For further information on who is required to lodge a Taxable payments "
"annual report refer to\n"
"https://softwaredevelopers.ato.gov.au/tprs\n"
"\n"
"The annual report must be provided to the Commissioner no later than 28 "
"August after the end of the financial year. Reports can be sent more "
"frequently for those that wish to do so.\n"
"\n"
"The report uses tax tags ``Service`` and ``Tax Withheld`` in order to find "
"adequate journal items. These are set using the fiscal positions, and the "
"right type of product (Services).\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Bogføringsmodul for Australien\n"
"============================\n"
"\n"
"Årsrapporter om skattepligtige betalinger (TPAR) for Australien\n"
"\n"
"Den årlige rapport om skattepligtige betalinger (TPAR) gør det muligt at "
"rapportere:\n"
"\n"
"    • betalinger til entreprenører eller underentreprenører for "
"tjenesteydelser eller\n"
"    • tilskud udbetalt af offentlige enheder til ABN-indehavere\n"
"\n"
"i henhold til systemet for rapportering af skattepligtige betalinger (TPRS) "
"og reglerne for rapportering af skattepligtige offentlige tilskud og "
"betalinger.\n"
"\n"
"TPAR skal indsendes senest den 28. august hvert år.\n"
"\n"
"Manglende rettidig indsendelse af TPAR kan medføre bøder.\n"
"\n"
"For yderligere oplysninger om, hvem der skal indsende en årsrapport om "
"skattepligtige betalinger, se:\n"
"https://softwaredevelopers.ato.gov.au/tprs\n"
"\n"
"Årsrapporten skal indsendes til kommissæren senest den 28. august efter "
"regnskabsårets afslutning. Det er muligt at indsende rapporter oftere, hvis "
"ønsket.\n"
"\n"
"Rapporten bruger skattetags ``service`` og ``kildeskat`` til at finde de "
"rette journalposter, som indstilles via finansielle positioner og den rette "
"produkttype (service).\n"

