#. module: base
#: model:ir.module.module,description:base.module_l10n_cl_edi
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"\n"
"EDI Chilean Localization\n"
"========================\n"
"This module facilitates the generation of DTE (Electronic Taxable Document) "
"for Chilean invoicing. Key features include:\n"
"- DTE Format in XML: The document is structured in XML format for "
"standardized electronic transactions.\n"
"- Direct Communication with SII: Enables direct interaction with the "
"Servicio de Impuestos Internos (SII) to send invoices and other tax "
"documents related to sales.\n"
"- Customer Communication: Sends sales DTEs to customers.\n"
"- Supplier Communication: Accepts DTEs from suppliers (vendors).\n"
"- SII Notifications: Informs SII about the acceptance or rejection of vendor "
"bills or other DTEs.\n"
"\n"
"Note: To display barcodes on invoices, the `pdf417gen` library is required.\n"
"\n"
"Electronic Receipts Compliance\n"
"==============================\n"
"\n"
"As per SII requirements, starting March 2021, all boletas transactions must "
"be sent to SII using a different web service than the one used for "
"electronic invoices. Previously, only a daily report was required.\n"
"\n"
"Recent Changes\n"
"==============\n"
"\n"
"- Elimination of Daily Sales Book Requirement: As of August 1st, 2022, the "
"daily sales book (\"Libro de ventas diarias\") is no longer required by the "
"authorities and has been removed from this version of Odoo.\n"
"\n"
"Differences between Electronic Boletas and Electronic Invoicing Workflows\n"
"=========================================================================\n"
"\n"
"1. Dedicated Servers for Boletas:\n"
"- Production environment: `palena.sii.cl`\n"
"- Test environment: `maullin.sii.cl`\n"
"\n"
"2. Different Authentication and Status Services:\n"
"- Authentication services and methods for querying delivery and document "
"status differ between electronic boletas and electronic invoices.\n"
"\n"
"3. Authentication Token:\n"
"- The process for obtaining authentication tokens varies.\n"
"\n"
"4. Updated XML Schema:\n"
"- New tags have been incorporated into the XML schema for electronic "
"boletas.\n"
"\n"
"5. Validation Diagnosis:\n"
"- Electronic boletas receive validation diagnoses through a REST web service "
"using the delivery track-id.\n"
"- Electronic invoices continue to receive diagnoses via email.\n"
"\n"
"6. Track-ID Length:\n"
"- Electronic boletas: 15 digits\n"
"- Electronic invoices: 10 digits\n"
"\n"
"For detailed guidance, refer to the [SII Guide](https://www.sii.cl/"
"factura_electronica/factura_mercado/Instructivo_Emision_Boleta_Elect.pdf).\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"EDI – chilensk lokalisering\n"
"========================\n"
"Dette modul forenkler genereringen af DTE (elektronisk skattepligtigt "
"dokument) til chilensk fakturering. Nøglefunktioner omfatter:\n"
"- DTE i XML-format: Dokumentet er struktureret i XML til standardiserede "
"elektroniske transaktioner.\n"
"- Direkte kommunikation med SII: Muliggør direkte interaktion med Servicio "
"de Impuestos Internos (SII) for afsendelse af fakturaer og andre "
"skattedokumenter relateret til salg.\n"
"- Kundekommunikation: Sender salgs-DTE’er til kunder.\n"
"- Leverandørkommunikation: Modtager og accepterer DTE’er fra leverandører "
"(forhandlere).\n"
"- SII-meddelelser: Informerer SII om accept eller afvisning af "
"leverandørfakturaer og andre DTE’er.\n"
"\n"
"Bemærk: For at stregkoder kan vises på fakturaer kræves biblioteket "
"`pdf417gen`.\n"
"\n"
"Overholdelse af regler for elektroniske kvitteringer\n"
"==============================\n"
"\n"
"I henhold til SII-kravene skal alle boletas-transaktioner fra marts 2021 "
"sendes til SII via en anden webservice end den, der anvendes til "
"elektroniske fakturaer. Tidligere var det kun nødvendigt at indsende en "
"daglig rapport.\n"
"\n"
"Nylige ændringer\n"
"==============\n"
"\n"
"- Afskaffelse af kravet om daglig salgsbog: Fra 1. august 2022 kræver "
"myndighederne ikke længere en daglig salgsbog (\"Libro de ventas diarias\"), "
"og denne er derfor fjernet i denne version af Odoo.\n"
"\n"
"Forskelle mellem elektroniske boletas og elektroniske faktureringsworkflows\n"
"=========================================================================\n"
"\n"
"1. Dedikerede servere til boletas:\n"
"- Produktionsmiljø: `palena.sii.cl`\n"
"- Testmiljø: `maullin.sii.cl`\n"
"\n"
"2. Forskellige godkendelses- og statustjenester:\n"
"- Godkendelsestjenester og metoder til forespørgsler om leverings- og "
"dokumentstatus adskiller sig mellem elektroniske boletas og elektroniske "
"fakturaer.\n"
"\n"
"3. Godkendelsestoken:\n"
"- Processen for at opnå godkendelsestokens varierer mellem boletas og "
"fakturaer.\n"
"\n"
"4. Opdateret XML-skema:\n"
"- Nye tags er blevet tilføjet i XML-skemaet for elektroniske boletas.\n"
"\n"
"5. Valideringsdiagnose:\n"
"- Elektroniske boletas modtager valideringsdiagnoser via en REST-webservice "
"ved hjælp af leverings-track-ID’et.\n"
"- Elektroniske fakturaer modtager fortsat diagnoser via e-mail.\n"
"\n"
"6. Track-ID'ets længde:\n"
"- Elektroniske boletas: 15 cifre\n"
"- Elektroniske fakturaer: 10 cifre\n"
"\n"
"For detaljeret vejledning henvises til [SII Guide](https://www.sii.cl/"
"factura_electronica/factura_mercado/Instructivo_Emision_Boleta_Elect.pdf).\n"
"\n"

