#. module: base
#: model:ir.module.module,description:base.module_l10n_eu_oss
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"\n"
"EU One Stop Shop (OSS) VAT\n"
"==========================\n"
"\n"
"From July 1st 2021, EU businesses that are selling goods within the EU above "
"EUR 10 000 to buyers located in another EU Member State need to register and "
"pay VAT in the buyers’ Member State.\n"
"Below this new EU-wide threshold you can continue to apply the domestic "
"rules for VAT on your cross-border sales. In order to simplify the "
"application of this EU directive, the One Stop Shop (OSS) registration "
"scheme allows businesses to make a unique tax declaration.\n"
"\n"
"This module makes it possible by helping with the creation of the required "
"EU fiscal positions and taxes in order to automatically apply and record the "
"required taxes.\n"
"\n"
"All you have to do is check that the proposed mapping is suitable for the "
"products and services you sell.\n"
"\n"
"References\n"
"++++++++++\n"
"Council Directive (EU) 2017/2455 Council Directive (EU) 2019/1995\n"
"Council Implementing Regulation (EU) 2019/2026\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"EU's One Stop Shop (OSS) moms\n"
"==========================\n"
"\n"
"Fra 1. juli 2021 skal EU-virksomheder, der sælger varer inden for EU for "
"over 10.000 EUR til købere i en anden EU-medlemsstat, registrere sig og "
"betale moms i køberens medlemsstat.\n"
"Inden for denne nye EU-dækkende tærskel kan du stadig anvende de nationale "
"momsregler på dit grænseoverskridende salg. For at forenkle implementeringen "
"af direktivet giver One Stop Shop (OSS)-registreringsordningen virksomheder "
"mulighed for at indsende en samlet afgiftsangivelse.\n"
"\n"
"Dette modul understøtter processen ved at hjælpe med oprettelsen af de "
"nødvendige EU-skattestillinger og -afgifter, så afgifter automatisk kan "
"anvendes og registreres.\n"
"\n"
"Du skal blot sikre, at den foreslåede kortlægning passer til de produkter og "
"tjenester, du sælger.\n"
"\n"
"Referencer\n"
"++++++++++\n"
"Rådets direktiv (EU) 2017/2455 Rådets direktiv (EU) 2019/1995\n"
"Rådets gennemførelsesforordning (EU) 2019/2026\n"
"\n"

