#. module: base
#: model:ir.module.module,description:base.module_l10n_in
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"\n"
"Indian Accounting: Chart of Account.\n"
"====================================\n"
"\n"
"Indian accounting chart and localization.\n"
"\n"
"Odoo allows to manage Indian Accounting by providing Two Formats Of Chart of "
"Accounts i.e Indian Chart Of Accounts - Standard and Indian Chart Of "
"Accounts - Schedule VI.\n"
"\n"
"Note: The Schedule VI has been revised by MCA and is applicable for all "
"Balance Sheet made after\n"
"31st March, 2011. The Format has done away with earlier two options of "
"format of Balance\n"
"Sheet, now only Vertical format has been permitted Which is Supported By "
"Odoo.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Indisk bogføring: Kontoplan.\n"
"====================================\n"
"\n"
"Indisk regnskabsskema og lokalisering.\n"
"\n"
"Odoo understøtter indisk regnskab ved at tilbyde to formater for "
"kontoplaner: Indisk kontoplan – Standard og Indisk kontoplan – Skema VI.\n"
"\n"
"Bemærk: VI er blevet revideret af MCA (Ministry of Corporate Affairs) og "
"gælder for alle statusopgørelser udarbejdet efter\n"
"31. marts 2011. Det reviderede skema har afskaffet de to tidligere formater "
"for statusopgørelser,\n"
"og kun det lodrette format er nu tilladt, hvilket fuldt ud understøttes af "
"Odoo.\n"

