#. module: base
#: model:ir.module.module,description:base.module_l10n_ca
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"\n"
"This is the module to manage the Canadian accounting chart in Odoo.\n"
"===========================================================================================\n"
"\n"
"Canadian accounting charts and localizations.\n"
"\n"
"Fiscal positions\n"
"----------------\n"
"\n"
"When considering taxes to be applied, it is the province where the delivery "
"occurs that matters.\n"
"Therefore we decided to implement the most common case in the fiscal "
"positions: delivery is the\n"
"responsibility of the vendor and done at the customer location.\n"
"\n"
"Some examples:\n"
"\n"
"1) You have a customer from another province and you deliver to his "
"location.\n"
"On the customer, set the fiscal position to his province.\n"
"\n"
"2) You have a customer from another province. However this customer comes to "
"your location\n"
"with their truck to pick up products. On the customer, do not set any fiscal "
"position.\n"
"\n"
"3) An international vendor doesn't charge you any tax. Taxes are charged at "
"customs\n"
"by the customs broker. On the vendor, set the fiscal position to "
"International.\n"
"\n"
"4) An international vendor charge you your provincial tax. They are "
"registered with your\n"
"position.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Dette modul bruges til at administrere canadiske kontoplaner i Odoo.\n"
"===========================================================================================\n"
"\n"
"Canadisk kontoplan og lokalisering.\n"
"\n"
"Skattepositioner\n"
"----------------\n"
"\n"
"Når man ser på, hvilke skatter der skal anvendes, afhænger det af den "
"provins, hvor leveringen finder sted.\n"
"Derfor har vi valgt at implementere det mest almindelige scenarie i "
"skattepositionerne: Leveringen sker\n"
"på kundens adresse og er leverandørens ansvar.\n"
"\n"
"Eksempler:\n"
"\n"
"1) Du har en kunde fra en anden provins, og leveringen sker til kundens "
"adresse.\n"
"Indstil skattepositionen for kunden til kundens provins.\n"
"\n"
"2) Du har en kunde fra en anden provins, men kunden afhenter selv\n"
"produkterne på din adresse. Indstil ikke en skatteposition for kunden.\n"
"\n"
"3) En international leverandør fakturerer dig ikke skatter. Skatterne "
"opkræves\n"
"af toldagenten ved grænsen.\n"
"Indstil skattepositionen for leverandøren til \"International\".\n"
"\n"
"4) En international leverandør opkræver din provinsafgift. Du er registreret "
"med din\n"
"adresse.\n"

#. module: base
#: model:ir.module.module,description:base.module_l10n_pl
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
