#. module: base
#: model:ir.module.module,description:base.module_account_sepa_direct_debit
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"\n"
"This module enables the generation of SEPA Direct Debit (SDD)-compliant XML "
"files (consistent\n"
"with pain.008.001.02 specification) to send to your bank in order to\n"
"collect a set of payments.\n"
"\n"
"To be eligible for this payment method, a customer must have first\n"
"returned a mandate to the company, giving their consent to use direct "
"debit.\n"
"This consent must have been encoded as a 'customer mandate' in Odoo.\n"
"\n"
"You also need to meet the following requirements in order to properly\n"
"generate an SDD file:\n"
"- Your company account must be set to a valid IBAN number\n"
"- Your company must have been given a creditor identifier (this can be done "
"in Settings - General Settings - Accounting section)\n"
"- Your company must have defined a journal to receive SDD payments (again, "
"in 'settings' of accounting module)\n"
"- Every customer for whom you generate a payment must have a valid IBAN "
"account number.\n"
"\n"
"Odoo will let you know if any of these requirements are not satisfied.\n"
"\n"
"To register a payment for open invoices, you can use the dedicated\n"
"'SEPA Direct Debit' option by selecting a bank account in the 'Register\n"
"Payment' wizard. An error message will appear if no valid mandate is\n"
"available for generating a payment on the selected invoice.\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"Dette modul gør det muligt at generere XML-filer i overensstemmelse med SEPA-"
"betalingsaftaler for direkte debitering (SDD) i henhold\n"
"til pain.008.001.02-specifikationen), så filerne kan sendes til banken med "
"henblik på\n"
"inddrivelse af flere betalinger.\n"
"\n"
"For at kunne benytte denne betalingsform skal kunden først\n"
"have givet virksomheden et mandat, hvori der gives samtykke til direkte "
"debitering.\n"
"Dette samtykke skal være registreret i Odoo som et 'kundemandat'.\n"
"\n"
"Derudover skal følgende betingelser være opfyldt for korrekt\n"
"oprettelse af en SDD-fil:\n"
"- Virksomhedens bankkonto skal have et gyldigt IBAN-nummer\n"
"- Virksomheden skal have modtaget et kreditoridentifikationsnummer (kan "
"angives under Indstillinger - Generelle indstillinger - Bogføring)\n"
"- Der skal være angivet en journal til modtagelse af SDD-betalinger (i "
"bogføringsmodulets indstillinger)\n"
"- Hver kunde, som der oprettes en betaling for, skal have et gyldigt IBAN-"
"nummer.\n"
"\n"
"Odoo giver besked, hvis et eller flere af disse krav ikke er opfyldt.\n"
"\n"
"For at registrere betalinger for åbne fakturaer kan du anvende "
"betalingsformn\n"
"'SEPA-direkte debitering' ved at vælge en bankkonto i guiden 'Registrér\n"
"betaling'. Hvis der ikke findes et gyldigt mandat for\n"
"den valgte faktura, vises en fejlmeddelelse.\n"

#. module: base
