#. module: base
#: model:ir.module.module,description:base.module_website_blog
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Odoo Blog\n"
"----------\n"
"\n"
"Write, Design, Promote and Engage with <a href=\"https://www.odoo.com/app/"
"blog\">Odoo Blog</a>.\n"
"\n"
"Express yourself with the Odoo enterprise grade blogging platform. Write\n"
"beautiful blog posts, engage with visitors, translate content and moderate\n"
"social streams.\n"
"\n"
"Get your blog posts efficiently referenced in Google and translated in "
"mutiple\n"
"languages in just a few clicks.\n"
"\n"
"Write Beautiful Blog Posts\n"
"--------------------------\n"
"\n"
"Drag & Drop well designed *'Building Blocks'* to create beautifull blog "
"posts\n"
"that perfectly integrates images, videos, call-to-actions, quotes, banners,\n"
"etc.\n"
"\n"
"With our unique *'edit inline'* approach, you don't need to be a designer "
"to\n"
"create awsome, good-looking, content. Each blog post will look like it's\n"
"designed by a professional designer.\n"
"\n"
"Automated Translation by Professionals\n"
"--------------------------------------\n"
"\n"
"Get your blog posts translated in multiple languages with no effort. Our\n"
"translation \"on demand\" feature allows you to benefit from professional\n"
"translators to translate all your changes automatically. (\\$0.05 per word)\n"
"Translated versions are updated automatically once translated by "
"professionals\n"
"(around 32 hours).\n"
"\n"
"Engage With Your Visitors\n"
"-------------------------\n"
"\n"
"The integrated website live chat feature allows you to start chatting in "
"real time with\n"
"your visitors to get feedback on your recent posts or get ideas to write "
"new\n"
"posts.\n"
"\n"
"Engaging with your visitors is also a great way to convert visitors into\n"
"customers.\n"
"\n"
"Build Visitor Loyalty\n"
"---------------------\n"
"\n"
"The one click *follow* button will allow visitors to receive your blog posts "
"by\n"
"email with no effort, without having to register. Social media icons allow\n"
"visitors to share your best blog posts easily.\n"
"\n"
"Google Analytics Integration\n"
"----------------------------\n"
"\n"
"Get a clear visibility of your sales funnel. Odoo's Google Analytics "
"trackers\n"
"are configured by default to track all kinds of events related to shopping\n"
"carts, call-to-actions, etc.\n"
"\n"
"As Odoo marketing tools (mass mailing, campaigns, etc) are also linked with\n"
"Google Analytics, you get a 360° view of your business.\n"
"\n"
"SEO Optimized Blog Posts\n"
"------------------------\n"
"\n"
"SEO tools are ready to use, with no configuration required. Odoo suggests\n"
"keywords for your titles according to Google's most searched terms, Google\n"
"Analytics tracks interests of your visitors, sitemaps are created "
"automatically\n"
"for quick Google indexing, etc.\n"
"\n"
"The system even creates structured content automatically to promote your\n"
"products and events effectively in Google.\n"
"\n"
"Designer-Friendly Themes\n"
"------------------------\n"
"\n"
"Themes are awesome and easy to design. You don't need to develop to create "
"new\n"
"pages, themes or building blocks. We use a clean HTML structure, a\n"
"[bootstrap](http://getbootstrap.com/) CSS and our modularity allows you to\n"
"distribute your themes easily.\n"
"\n"
"The building block approach allows the website to remain clean after end-"
"users\n"
"start creating new contents.\n"
"\n"
"Easy Access Rights\n"
"------------------\n"
"\n"
"Not everyone requires the same access to your website. Designers manage the\n"
"layout of the site, editors approve content and authors write that content.\n"
"This lets you organize your publishing process according to your needs.\n"
"\n"
"Other access rights are related to business objects (products, people, "
"events,\n"
"etc) and directly following Odoo's standard access rights management, so you "
"do\n"
"not have to configure things twice.\n"
msgstr ""
"Odoo Blog\n"
"----------\n"
"\n"
"Skriv, design, promovér og interagér med din <a href=\"https://www.odoo.com/"
"app/blog\">Odoo Blog</a>.\n"
"\n"
"Gør dine budskaber levende med Odoos blogplatform til virksomheder. Skriv\n"
"flotte blogindlæg, interagér med dine besøgende, oversæt indhold og "
"administrér\n"
"sociale feeds.\n"
"\n"
"Få nemt dine blogindlæg indekseret af Google og oversat til flere\n"
"sprog med få klik.\n"
"\n"
"Skriv flotte blogindlæg\n"
"--------------------------\n"
"\n"
"Træk og slip færdige ‘designmoduler’ for at skabe smukke blogindlæg,\n"
"der integrerer billeder, videoer, opfordringer til handling, citater, "
"bannere\n"
"m.m. perfekt.\n"
"\n"
"Med vores entydige *'redigér inline'*-funktion behøver du ikke være designer "
"for at\n"
"skabe flot og fængende indhold. Hvert blogindlæg får et professionelt\n"
"designet udseende.\n"
"\n"
"Automatisk oversættelse af professionelle\n"
"--------------------------------------\n"
"\n"
"Få dine blogindlæg oversat til flere sprog uden besvær. Med vores\n"
"\"on demand\"-oversættelsesfunktion kan professionelle oversættere\n"
"automatisk omsætte alle dine ændringer (0,05 $ pr. ord).\n"
"De oversatte versioner opdateres automatisk\n"
"(typisk inden for ca. 32 timer).\n"
"\n"
"Interagér med dine besøgende\n"
"-------------------------\n"
"\n"
"Den integrerede livechat på din hjemmeside giver dig mulighed for at tale "
"direkte\n"
"med dine besøgende i realtid – få feedback på dine seneste indlæg eller "
"idéer til\n"
"nye.\n"
"\n"
"At engagere dine besøgende er også en effektiv måde at omsætte dem til\n"
"kunder på.\n"
"\n"
"Opbyg loyalitet hos besøgende\n"
"---------------------\n"
"\n"
"Med et enkelt klik på *følg*-knappen kan dine besøgende modtage dine "
"blogindlæg direkte i deres\n"
"indbakke – helt uden besvær og uden registrering. Sociale medie-ikoner gør "
"det desuden\n"
"nemt at dele dine bedste indlæg.\n"
"\n"
"Integration med Google Analytics\n"
"----------------------------\n"
"\n"
"Få et tydeligt overblik over din salgstragt. Odoos Google Analytics-"
"trackere\n"
"er som standard indstillet til at spore alle begivenheder i forbindelse med\n"
"indkøbskurve, handlingsopfordringer og meget mere.\n"
"\n"
"Da Odoos marketingværktøjer (som masseforsendelser og kampagner) også er "
"integreret med\n"
"Google Analytics, får du et komplet 360°-overblik over din virksomhed.\n"
"\n"
"SEO-optimerede blogindlæg\n"
"------------------------\n"
"\n"
"SEO-værktøjer er klar til brug uden opsætning. Odoo foreslår relevante\n"
"søgeord til dine titler baseret på Googles mest søgte termer, sporer dine "
"besøgendes interesser via Google\n"
"Analytics, og opretter automatisk\n"
"sitemaps for hurtig indeksering på Google.\n"
"\n"
"Systemet genererer endda automatisk struktureret indhold, så dine\n"
"produkter og begivenheder bliver effektivt promoveret på Google.\n"
"\n"
"Designervenlige temaer\n"
"------------------------\n"
"\n"
"Temaerne er flotte og nemme at arbejde med. Du behøver ikke erfaring som "
"udvikler for at oprette nye\n"
"sider, temaer eller designmoduler. Vi bruger en ren\n"
"[bootstrap](http://getbootstrap.com/) CSS, og vores modulære design gør det "
"let at\n"
"distribuere dine temaer.\n"
"\n"
"Tilgangen med designmoduler sikrer, at dit websted forbliver overskueligt, "
"selv når slutbrugerne\n"
"begynder at oprette nyt indhold.\n"
"\n"
"Nemme adgangsrettigheder\n"
"------------------\n"
"\n"
"Ikke alle behøver samme adgang til din hjemmeside. Designere styrer sidens\n"
"layout, redaktører godkender indhold, og forfattere står for at skrive "
"indholdet.\n"
"På den måde kan du tilpasse udgivelsesprocessen efter dine behov.\n"
"\n"
"Andre adgangsrettigheder knytter sig til forretningsobjekter (produkter, "
"personer, begivenheder\n"
"osv.) og følger Odoos standardstyring af adgangsrettigheder, så du\n"
"slipper for at konfigurere det dobbelt.\n"

#. module: base
#: model:ir.module.module,description:base.module_crm
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Odoo CRM\n"
"--------\n"
"\n"
"Boost sales productivity, improve win rates, grow revenue with the Odoo\n"
"<a href=\"https://www.odoo.com/app/crm\">Open Source CRM</a>.\n"
"\n"
"Manage your sales funnel with no effort. Attract leads, follow-up on phone\n"
"calls and meetings. Analyse the quality of your leads to make informed\n"
"decisions and save time by integrating emails directly into the "
"application.\n"
"\n"
"Your Sales Funnel, The Way You Like It\n"
"--------------------------------------\n"
"\n"
"Track your opportunities pipeline with the revolutionary kanban view. Work\n"
"inside your sales funnel and get instant visual information about next "
"actions,\n"
"new messages, top opportunities and expected revenues.\n"
"\n"
"Lead Management Made Easy\n"
"-------------------------\n"
"\n"
"Create leads automatically from incoming emails. Analyse leads efficiency "
"and\n"
"compare performance by campaigns, channels or Sales Team.\n"
"\n"
"Find duplicates, merge leads and assign them to the right salesperson in "
"one\n"
"operation. Spend less time on administration and more time on qualifying "
"leads.\n"
"\n"
"Organize Your Opportunities\n"
"---------------------------\n"
"\n"
"Get your opportunities organized to stay focused on the best deals. Manage "
"all\n"
"your customer interactions from the opportunity like emails, phone calls,\n"
"internal notes, meetings and quotations.\n"
"\n"
"Follow opportunities that interest you to get notified upon specific "
"events:\n"
"deal won or lost, stage changed, new customer demand, etc.\n"
"\n"
"Email Integration and Automation\n"
"--------------------------------\n"
"\n"
"Work with the email applications you already use every day. Whether your\n"
"company uses Microsoft Outlook or Gmail, no one needs to change the way "
"they\n"
"work, so everyone stays productive.\n"
"\n"
"Route, sort and filter incoming emails automatically. Odoo CRM handles "
"incoming\n"
"emails and route them to the right opportunities or Sales Team. New leads "
"are\n"
"created on the fly and interested salespersons are notified automatically.\n"
"\n"
"Collaborative Agenda\n"
"--------------------\n"
"\n"
"Schedule your meetings and phone calls using the integrated calendar. You "
"can\n"
"see your agenda and your colleagues' in one view. As a manager, it's easy "
"to\n"
"see what your team is busy with.\n"
"\n"
"Lead Automation and Marketing Campaigns\n"
"---------------------------------------\n"
"\n"
"Drive performance by automating tasks with Odoo <a href=\"https://"
"www.odoo.com/app/crm\">CRM</a>.\n"
"\n"
"Use our marketing campaigns to automate lead acquisition, follow ups and\n"
"promotions. Define automation rules (e.g. ask a salesperson to call, send "
"an\n"
"email, ...) based on triggers (no activity since 20 days, answered a\n"
"promotional email, etc.)\n"
"\n"
"Optimize campaigns from lead to close, on every channel. Make smarter "
"decisions\n"
"about where to invest and show the impact of your marketing activities on "
"your\n"
"company's bottom line.\n"
"\n"
"Customize Your Sales Cycle\n"
"--------------------------\n"
"\n"
"Customize your sales cycle by configuring sales stages that perfectly fit "
"your\n"
"sales approach. Control statistics to get accurate forecasts to improve "
"your\n"
"sales performance at every stage of your customer relationship.\n"
"\n"
"Drive Engagement with Gamification\n"
"----------------------------------\n"
"\n"
"### Leverage your team's natural desire for competition\n"
"\n"
"Reinforce good habits and improve win rates with real-time recognition and\n"
"rewards inspired by [game mechanics](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"Gamification).\n"
"Align Sales Teams around clear business objectives with challenges, "
"personal\n"
"objectives and team leader boards.\n"
"\n"
"### Leaderboards\n"
"\n"
"Promote leaders and competition amongst Sales Team with performance ratios.\n"
"\n"
"### Personal Objectives\n"
"\n"
"Assign clear goals to users to align them with the company objectives.\n"
"\n"
"### Team Targets\n"
"\n"
"Compare revenues with forecasts and budgets in real time.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"Odoo CRM\n"
"--------\n"
"\n"
"Øg salgsproduktiviteten, forbedr succesraten og øg omsætningen med Odoo\n"
"<a href=\"https://www.odoo.com/app/crm\">Open Source CRM</a>.\n"
"\n"
"Administrér din salgstragt uden besvær. Tiltræk leads, følg op på\n"
"opkald og møder, og analysér kvaliteten af dine leads for at træffe "
"velinformerede\n"
"beslutninger. Spar tid ved at integrere e-mails direkte i appen.\n"
"\n"
"Din salgstragt, som du ønsker den\n"
"--------------------------------------\n"
"\n"
"Spor dine salgsmuligheder med den banebrydende Kanban-visning. Arbejd\n"
"direkte i salgstragten, og få øjeblikkelig visuel information om næste "
"handlinger,\n"
"nye beskeder, de mest lovende salgsmuligheder og forventede indtægter.\n"
"\n"
"Nem leadhåndtering\n"
"-------------------------\n"
"\n"
"Opret automatisk leads ud fra indgående e-mails. Analysér deres "
"effektivitet, og\n"
"sammenlign resultater på tværs af kampagner, kanaler eller salgsteams.\n"
"\n"
"Find dubletter, slå leads sammen, og tildel dem til den rigtige sælger – alt "
"på én\n"
"gang. Brug mindre tid på administration og mere tid på at kvalificere dine "
"leads.\n"
"\n"
"Organisér dine salgsmuligheder\n"
"---------------------------\n"
"\n"
"Organisér dine salgsmuligheder, så du kan fokusere på de mest lovende "
"tilbud. Administrér alle\n"
"dine kundeinteraktioner direkte fra salgsmuligheden – e-mails, opkald,\n"
"interne noter, møder og tilbud.\n"
"\n"
"Følg de salgsmuligheder, der interesserer dig, og få besked om specifikke "
"begivenheder\n"
"– eksempelvis vundet eller tabt aftale, ændret fase, nye kundekrav med "
"mere.\n"
"\n"
"E-mail-integration og automatisering\n"
"--------------------------------\n"
"\n"
"Brug de e-mailprogrammer, du allerede kender. Uanset om virksomheden\n"
"bruger Microsoft Outlook eller Gmail, behøver ingen ændre deres "
"arbejdsmetoder,\n"
"\n"
"så alle kan fortsætte med at arbejde produktivt.\n"
"\n"
"Dirigér, sortér og filtrér indgående e-mails automatisk. Odoo CRM håndterer "
"dem og sender\n"
"dem videre til de rette salgsmuligheder eller salgsteams. Nye leads "
"oprettes\n"
"med det samme, og de relevante sælgere får automatisk besked.\n"
"\n"
"Fælles kalender\n"
"--------------------\n"
"\n"
"Planlæg dine møder og opkald med den integrerede kalender. Få overblik\n"
"over både din egen og dine kollegers dagsorden. Som leder er det let at se,\n"
"hvad dit team arbejder med.\n"
"\n"
"Leadautomatisering og marketingkampagner\n"
"---------------------------------------\n"
"\n"
"Øg effektiviteten ved at automatisere opgaver med Odoo <a href=\"https://"
"www.odoo.com/app/crm\">CRM</a>.\n"
"\n"
"Brug vores marketingkampagner til at automatisere kundeanskaffelse, "
"opfølgning og\n"
"kampagner. Definér automatiseringsregler – f.eks. bed en sælger om at ringe "
"eller sende en\n"
"e-mail – baseret på triggere som ingen aktivitet i 20 dage eller besvarelse "
"af en\n"
"kampagne-e-mail.\n"
"\n"
"Optimér dine kampagner fra lead til afslutning på tværs af alle kanaler. Tag "
"smartere\n"
"beslutninger om,\n"
"hvor du skal investere, og få indsigt i, hvordan dine\n"
"marketingaktiviteter påvirker virksomhedens bundlinje.\n"
"\n"
"Tilpas din salgscyklus\n"
"--------------------------\n"
"\n"
"Tilpas din salgscyklus ved at konfigurere salgsfaser, der passer til din\n"
"strategi. Følg statistikkerne for at få præcise prognoser og forbedre din\n"
"salgsperformance gennem hele kundeforløbet.\n"
"\n"
"Fremme engagement med gamification\n"
"----------------------------------\n"
"\n"
"### Udnyt teamets naturlige konkurrenceinstinkt.\n"
"\n"
"Styrk gode vaner og øg vinderprocenten med realtids-feedback og\n"
"belønninger inspireret af gamification(http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"Gamification).\n"
"Saml salgsteams omkring klare forretningsmål gennem udfordringer, "
"personlige\n"
"mål og team-ranglister.\n"
"\n"
"### Ranglister\n"
"\n"
"Styrk lederskab og konkurrence blandt salgsteamet gennem "
"præstationsratioer.\n"
"\n"
"### Personlige målsætninger\n"
"\n"
"Tildel brugerne tydelige mål, så de stemmer overens med virksomhedens "
"overordnede mål.\n"
"\n"
"### Teamets målsætninger\n"
"\n"
"Sammenlign indtægter med prognoser og budgetter i realtid.\n"
"\n"

