msgstr "Odoo Proprietær Licens v1,0"

#. module: base
#: model:ir.module.module,description:base.module_purchase
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Odoo Supply Chain\n"
"-----------------\n"
"\n"
"Automate requisition-to-pay, control invoicing with the Odoo\n"
"<a href=\"https://www.odoo.com/app/purchase\">Open Source Supply Chain</a>.\n"
"\n"
"Automate procurement propositions, launch request for quotations, track\n"
"purchase orders, manage vendors' information, control products reception "
"and\n"
"check vendors' invoices.\n"
"\n"
"Automated Procurement Propositions\n"
"----------------------------------\n"
"\n"
"Reduce inventory level with procurement rules. Get the right purchase\n"
"proposition at the right time to reduce your inventory level. Improve your\n"
"purchase and inventory performance with procurement rules depending on "
"stock\n"
"levels, logistic rules, sales orders, forecasted manufacturing orders, etc.\n"
"\n"
"Send requests for quotations or purchase orders to your vendor in one "
"click.\n"
"Get access to product receptions and invoices from your purchase order.\n"
"\n"
"Purchase Tenders\n"
"----------------\n"
"\n"
"Launch purchase tenders, integrate vendor's answers in the process and\n"
"compare propositions. Choose the best offer and send purchase orders "
"easily.\n"
"Use reporting to analyse the quality of your vendors afterwards.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"Email integrations\n"
"------------------\n"
"\n"
"Integrate all vendor's communications on the purchase orders (or RfQs) to "
"get\n"
"a strong traceability on the negotiation or after sales service issues. Use "
"the\n"
"claim management module to track issues related to vendors.\n"
"\n"
"Standard Price, Average Price, FIFO\n"
"-----------------------------------\n"
"\n"
"Use the costing method that reflects your business: standard price, average\n"
"price, fifo or lifo. Get your accounting entries and the right inventory\n"
"valuation in real-time; Odoo manages everything for you, transparently.\n"
"\n"
"Import Vendor Pricelists\n"
"--------------------------\n"
"\n"
"Take smart purchase decisions using the best prices.  Easily import "
"vendor's\n"
"pricelists to make smarter purchase decisions based on promotions, prices\n"
"depending on quantities and special contract conditions. You can even base "
"your\n"
"sale price depending on your vendor's prices.\n"
"\n"
"Control Products and Invoices\n"
"-----------------------------\n"
"\n"
"No product or order is left behind, the inventory control allows you to "
"manage\n"
"back orders, refunds, product reception and quality control. Choose the "
"right\n"
"control method according to your need.\n"
"\n"
"Control vendor bills with no effort. Choose the right method according to\n"
"your need: pre-generate draft invoices based on purchase orders, on "
"products\n"
"receptions, create invoices manually and import lines from purchase orders,\n"
"etc.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"Odoo Forsyningskæde\n"
"-----------------\n"
"\n"
"Automatisér rekvisition-til-betaling, og få styr på faktureringen med Odoo\n"
"<a href=\"https://www.odoo.com/app/purchase\">open source-forsyningskæde</a>"
".\n"
"\n"
"Automatisér indkøbsforslag, udsend anmodninger om tilbud, spor\n"
"indkøbsordrer, administrér leverandørinformation samt kontrollér både "
"varemodtagelse og\n"
"leverandørfakturaer.\n"
"\n"
"Automatiserede indkøbsforslag\n"
"----------------------------------\n"
"\n"
"Reducér lagerbeholdningen med intelligente indkøbsregler. Få det rette "
"købstilbud\n"
"på det rette tidspunkt, og optimér lagerbindingen. Forbedr din\n"
"indkøbs- og lagerperformance med indkøbsregler baseret på lagerbeholdning,\n"
"logistikregler, salgsordrer, forventede produktionsordrer m.m.\n"
"\n"
"Send anmodninger om tilbud eller indkøbsordrer til dine leverandører med ét "
"enkelt klik.\n"
"Få direkte adgang til varemodtagelser og fakturaer fra indkøbsordren.\n"
"\n"
"Købstilbud\n"
"----------------\n"
"\n"
"Håndtér indkøbsudbud, integrér leverandørernes svar i processen, og\n"
"sammenlign nemt tilbud. Vælg det bedste tilbud, og send indkøbsordrer helt "
"uden besvær.\n"
"Brug rapportering til efterfølgende at analysere leverandørernes kvalitet.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"E-mailintegrationer\n"
"------------------\n"
"\n"
"Saml al kommunikation med leverandører direkte på indkøbsordrer (eller "
"RFQ’er) for at\n"
"sikre stærk sporbarhed i forbindelse med forhandlinger og eftersalgsservice. "
"Brug\n"
"reklamationsmodulet til at spore og håndtere leverandørrelaterede "
"problemer.\n"
"\n"
"Standardpris, gennemsnitspris, FIFO\n"
"-----------------------------------\n"
"\n"
"Vælg den omkostningsberegningsmetode, der passer til din virksomhed: "
"standardpris, gennemsnitspris,\n"
"FIFO eller LIFO. Få korrekte regnskabsposteringer og en retvisende "
"lageropgørelse\n"
"i realtid, mens Odoo håndterer det hele på en transparent måde.\n"
"\n"
"Importér leverandørprislister\n"
"--------------------------\n"
"\n"
"Træf bedre købsbeslutninger baseret på de bedste priser. Importér nemt\n"
"leverandørprislister, og optimér dine indkøb ud fra kampagner,\n"
"mængderabatter og særlige kontraktbetingelser. Du kan endda\n"
"fastsætte dine salgspriser baseret på leverandørernes priser.\n"
"\n"
"Kontrol af produkter og fakturaer\n"
"-----------------------------\n"
"\n"
"Ingen produkter eller ordrer bliver overset. Lagerstyringen giver dig "
"mulighed for at\n"
"håndtere restordrer, returneringer, varemodtagelse og kvalitetskontrol. Vælg "
"den\n"
"kontrolmetode, der passer bedst til dine behov.\n"
"\n"
"Nem kontrol af leverandørfakturaer. Vælg den metode, der passer til\n"
"dine behov: forudgenerér fakturakladder baseret på indkøbsordrer eller "
"varemodtagelser,\n"
"opret fakturaer manuelt, eller importér linjer direkte fra indkøbsordrer\n"
"og meget mere.\n"
"\n"

#. module: base
#: model:ir.module.module,description:base.module_website
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Odoo Website Builder\n"
"--------------------\n"
"\n"
"Get an awesome and <a href=\"https://www.odoo.com/app/website\">free "
"website</a>,\n"
"easily customizable with the Odoo <a href=\"https://www.odoo.com/app/"
"website\">website builder</a>.\n"
"\n"
"Create enterprise grade website with our super easy builder. Use finely\n"
"designed building blocks and edit everything inline.\n"
"\n"
"Benefit from out-of-the-box business features; e-Commerce, events, blogs, "
"jobs\n"
"announces, customer references, call-to-actions, etc.\n"
"\n"
"Edit Anything Inline\n"
"--------------------\n"
"\n"
"Create beautiful websites with no technical knowledge. Odoo's unique *'edit\n"
"inline'* approach makes website creation surprisingly easy. No more complex\n"
"backend; just click anywhere to change any content.\n"
"\n"
"\"Want to change the price of a product? or put it in bold? Want to change "
"a\n"
"blog title?\" Just click and change. What you see is what you get. Really.\n"
"\n"
"Awesome. Astonishingly Beautiful.\n"
"---------------------------------\n"
"\n"
"Odoo's building blocks allow to design modern websites that are not "
"possible\n"
"with traditional WYSIWYG page editors.\n"
"\n"
"Whether it's for products descriptions, blogs or static pages, you don't "
"need\n"
"to be a professional designer to create clean contents. Just drag and drop "
"and\n"
"customize predefined building blocks.\n"
"\n"
"Enterprise-Ready, out-of-the-box\n"
"--------------------------------\n"
"\n"
"Activate ready-to-use enterprise features in just a click; e-commerce,\n"
"call-to-actions, jobs announces, events, customer references, blogs, etc.\n"
"\n"
"Traditional eCommerce and CMS have poorly designed backends as it's not "
"their\n"
"core focus. With the Odoo integration, you benefit from the best management\n"
"software to follow-up on your orders, your jobs applicants, your leads, "
"etc.\n"
"\n"
"A Great Mobile Experience\n"
"-------------------------\n"
"\n"
"Get a mobile friendly website thanks to our responsive design based on\n"
"bootstrap. All your pages adapt automatically to the screen size. (mobile\n"
"phones, tablets, desktop) You don't have to worry about mobile contents, it\n"
"works by default.\n"
"\n"
"SEO tools at your finger tips\n"
"-----------------------------\n"
"\n"
"The *Promote* tool suggests keywords according to Google most searched "
"terms.\n"
"Search Engine Optimization tools are ready to use, with no configuration\n"
"required.\n"
"\n"
"Google Analytics tracks your shopping cart events by default. Sitemap and\n"
"structured content are created automatically for Google indexation.\n"
"\n"
"Multi-Languages Made Easy\n"
"-------------------------\n"
"\n"
"Get your website translated in multiple languages with no effort. Odoo "
"proposes\n"
"and propagates translations automatically across pages, following what you "
"edit\n"
"on the master page.\n"
"\n"
"Designer-Friendly Templates\n"
"---------------------------\n"
"\n"
"Templates are awesome and easy to design. You don't need to develop to "
"create\n"
"new pages, themes or building blocks. We use a clean HTML structure, a\n"
"[bootstrap](http://getbootstrap.com/) CSS.\n"
"\n"
"Customize every page on the fly with the integrated template editor. "
"Distribute\n"
"your work easily as an Odoo module.\n"
"\n"
"Fluid Grid Layouting\n"
"--------------------\n"
"\n"
"Design perfect pages by drag and dropping building blocks. Move and scale "
"them\n"
"to fit the layout you are looking for.\n"
"\n"
"Building blocks are based on a responsive, mobile friendly fluid grid "
"system\n"
"that appropriately scales up to 12 columns as the device or viewport size\n"
"increases.\n"
"\n"
"Professional Themes\n"
"-------------------\n"
"\n"
"Design a custom theme or reuse pre-defined themes to customize the look and\n"
"feel of your website.\n"
"\n"
"Test new color scheme easily; you can change your theme at any time in just "
"a\n"
"click.\n"
"\n"
"Integrated With Odoo Apps\n"
"-------------------------\n"
"\n"
"### e-Commerce\n"
"\n"
"Promote products, sell online, optimize visitors' shopping experience.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"### Blog\n"
"\n"
"Write news, attract new visitors, build customer loyalty.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"### Online Events\n"
"\n"
"Schedule, organize, promote or sell events online; conferences, trainings, "
"webinars, etc.\n"
msgstr ""
"Odoo Hjemmesideværktøj\n"
"--------------------\n"
"\n"
"Få en fantastisk og <a href=\"https://www.odoo.com/app/website\">gratis "
"hjemmeside</a>,\n"
"som nemt kan tilpasses med Odoos <a href=\"https://www.odoo.com/app/"
"website\">hjemmesideværktøj</a>.\n"
"\n"
"Byg nemt en hjemmeside til din virksomhed med vores intuitive builder. Brug "
"stilfulde designmoduler, og redigér alt direkte på siden.\n"
"\n"
"Udnyt færdige forretningsfunktioner som e-handel, events, blogs, "
"jobannoncer, kundereferencer og handlingsopfordringer m.m.\n"
"\n"
"Redigér alt direkte på siden\n"
"--------------------\n"
"\n"
"Opret smukke hjemmesider uden teknisk viden. Odoos entydige tilgang "
"*'redigér\n"
"direkte på siden'* gør det overraskende nemt at bygge hjemmesider. Ingen "
"kompleks\n"
"backend – klik blot, hvor du vil, for at ændre indholdet.\n"
"\n"
"\"Vil du ændre prisen på et produkt? Sætte det i fed skrift? Eller ændre en\n"
"logtitel? Bare klik og redigér – det, du ser, er det, du får. Virkelig.\n"
"\n"
"Fantastisk. Utroligt smukt.\n"
"---------------------------------\n"
"\n"
"Odoos designmoduler gør det muligt at designe moderne hjemmesider, som\n"
"traditionelle WYSIWYG-sideeditorer ikke kan skabe.\n"
"\n"
"Uanset om det er til produktbeskrivelser, blogs eller statiske sider, "
"behøver du ikke\n"
"være professionel designer for at skabe overskueligt indhold. Du skal blot "
"trække og\n"
"slippe og tilpasse de foruddefinerede designmoduler.\n"
"\n"
"Klar til brug med det samme\n"
"--------------------------------\n"
"\n"
"Aktivér brugsklare virksomhedsfeatures med ét klik: e-handel,\n"
"handlingsopfordringer, jobannoncer, events, kundereferencer, blogs m.m.\n"
"\n"
"Traditionelle e-handels- og CMS-systemer har ofte dårligt designede "
"backends, fordi det ikke er deres\n"
"primære fokus. Med Odoo-integrationen får du derimod fordelene ved den "
"bedste administrationssoftware\n"
"til at følge op på ordrer, jobansøgere, leads m.m.\n"
"\n"
"En fantastisk mobiloplevelse\n"
"-------------------------\n"
"\n"
"Få en mobilvenlig hjemmeside med vores responsive design baseret på\n"
"Bootstrap. Alle sider tilpasser sig automatisk til skærmstørrelsen (mobil,\n"
"tablet og desktop. Du behøver ikke bekymre dig om mobilindhold; det\n"
"fungerer som standard.\n"
"\n"
"SEO-værktøjer lige ved hånden\n"
"-----------------------------\n"
"\n"
"Værktøjet *Promote* foreslår søgeord baseret på de mest søgte termer på "
"Google.\n"
"SEO-værktøjerne er klar til brug uden behov for yderligere\n"
"konfiguration.\n"
"\n"
"Google Analytics sporer automatisk begivenheder i din indkøbskurv. Sitemap "
"og\n"
"struktureret indhold oprettes automatisk, så Google nemt kan indeksere din "
"side.\n"
"\n"
"Flere sprog – nemt og hurtigt\n"
"-------------------------\n"
"\n"
"Få din hjemmeside oversat til flere sprog uden besvær. Odoo foreslår\n"
"og opdaterer automatisk oversættelser på tværs af siderne i takt med, at du "
"redigerer\n"
"master-siden.\n"
"\n"
"Designervenlige skabeloner\n"
"---------------------------\n"
"\n"
"Skabeloner er fantastiske og nemme at designe. Du behøver ikke at udvikle\n"
"for at oprette nye sider, temaer eller designmoduler. Vi benytter en ren "
"HTML-struktur og\n"
"[bootstrap](http://getbootstrap.com/) CSS.\n"
"\n"
"Tilpas hver side på farten med den indbyggede skabeloneditor, og distribuér\n"
"dit arbejde nemt som et Odoo-modul.\n"
"\n"
"Flydende gitterlayout\n"
"--------------------\n"
"\n"
"Skab perfekte sider med træk-og-slip-byggesten. Flyt og skalér dem,\n"
"så du får det layout, du ønsker.\n"
"\n"
"Designmodulerne bygger på et responsivt, mobilvenligt flydende "
"gittersystem,\n"
"er kan skaleres op til 12 kolonner, afhængigt af enhedens eller\n"
"skærmens størrelse.\n"
"\n"
"Professionelle temaer\n"
"-------------------\n"
"\n"
"Design et brugerdefineret tema, eller genbrug foruddefinerede temaer for at "
"tilpasse udseendet og\n"
"følelsen af din hjemmeside.\n"
"\n"
"Test nemt nye farveskemaer, og skift dit tema når som helst med ét\n"
"klik.\n"
"\n"
"Integreret med Odoo Apps\n"
"-------------------------\n"
"\n"
"### e-Handel\n"
"\n"
"Markedsfør produkter, sælg online og optimér kundernes shoppingoplevelse.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"### Blog\n"
"\n"
"Skriv nyheder, tiltræk nye besøgende og opbyg kundeloyalitet.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"### Online arrangementer\n"
"\n"
"Planlæg, arrangér, promovér, og sælg begivenheder online – konferencer, "
"kurser, webinarer m.m.\n"

#. module: base
#: model:ir.module.module,description:base.module_website_sale
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Odoo e-Commerce\n"
"---------------\n"
"\n"
"### Optimize sales with an awesome online store.\n"
"\n"
"Odoo is an <a href=\"https://www.odoo.com/app/ecommerce\">Open Source "
"eCommerce</a>\n"
"unlike anything you have ever seen before. Get an awesome catalog of "
"products\n"
"and great product description pages.\n"
"\n"
"It's full-featured, integrated with your management software, fully\n"
"customizable and super easy.\n"
"\n"
"Create Awesome Product Pages\n"
"----------------------------\n"
"\n"
"Odoo's unique *'edit inline'* and building blocks approach makes product "
"pages\n"
"creation surprisingly easy. \"Want to change the price of a product? or put "
"it\n"
"in bold? Want to add a banner for a specific product?\" just click and "
"change.\n"
"What you see is what you get. Really.\n"
"\n"
"Drag & Drop well designed *'Building Blocks'* to create beautifull product\n"
"pages that your customer will love.\n"
"\n"
"Increase Your Revenue Per Order\n"
"-------------------------------\n"
"\n"
"The built-in cross-selling feature helps you offer extra products related "
"to\n"
"what the shopper put in his cart. (e.g. accessories)\n"
"\n"
"Odoo's upselling algorythm allows you to show visitors similar but more\n"
"expensive products than the one in view, with incentives.\n"
"\n"
"The inline editing feature allows you to easily change a price, launch a\n"
"promotion or fine tune the description of a product, in a just a click.\n"
"\n"
"A Clean Google Analytics Integration\n"
"------------------------------------\n"
"\n"
"Get a clear visibility of your sales funnel. Odoo's Google Analytics "
"trackers\n"
"are configured by default to track all kind of events related to shopping\n"
"carts, call-to-actions, etc.\n"
"\n"
"As Odoo marketing tools (mass mailing, campaigns, etc) are also linked with\n"
"Google Analytics, you get a complete view of your business.\n"
"\n"
"Target New Markets\n"
"------------------\n"
"\n"
"Get your website translated in multiple languages with no effort. Odoo "
"proposes\n"
"and propagates translations automatically across pages.\n"
"\n"
"Our translation \"on demand\" features allows you to benefit from "
"professional\n"
"translators to translate all your changes automatically. Just change any "
"part\n"
"of your website (a new blog post, a page modification, product "
"descriptions,\n"
"...) and the translated versions are updated automatically in around 32 "
"hours.\n"
"\n"
"Fine Tune Your Catalog\n"
"----------------------\n"
"\n"
"Get full control on how you display your products in the catalog page:\n"
"promotional ribbons, related size of products, discounts, variants, grid/"
"list\n"
"view, etc.\n"
"\n"
"Edit any product inline to make your website evolve with your customer "
"need.\n"
"\n"
"Acquire New Customers\n"
"---------------------\n"
"\n"
"SEO tools are ready to use, with no configuration required. Odoo suggests\n"
"keywords according to Google most searched terms, Google Analytics tracks "
"your\n"
"shopping cart events, sitemap are created automatically for Google "
"indexation,\n"
"etc.\n"
"\n"
"We even do structured content automatically to promote your product and "
"events\n"
"efficiently in Google.\n"
"\n"
"Leverage Social Media\n"
"---------------------\n"
"\n"
"Create new landing pages easily with the Odoo inline editing feature. Send\n"
"visitors of your different marketing campaigns to specific landing pages to\n"
"optimize conversions.\n"
"\n"
"Manage a Reseller Network\n"
"-------------------------\n"
"\n"
"Manage a reseller network to target new market, have local presences or "
"broaden\n"
"your distribution. Give them access to your reseller portal for an "
"efficient\n"
"collaboration.\n"
"\n"
"Promote your resellers online, forward leads to resellers (with built-in\n"
"geolocalisation feature), define specific pricelists, launch a loyalty "
"program\n"
"(offer specific discounts to your best customers or resellers), etc.\n"
"\n"
"Benefit from the power of Odoo, in your online store: a powerfull tax "
"engine,\n"
"flexible pricing structures, a real inventory management solution, a "
"reseller\n"
"interface, support for products with different behaviours; physical goods,\n"
"events, services, variants and options, etc.\n"
"\n"
"You don't need to interface with your warehouse, sales or accounting "
"software.\n"
"Everything is integrated with Odoo. No pain, real time.\n"
"\n"
"A Clean Checkout Process\n"
"------------------------\n"
"\n"
"Convert most visitor interests into real orders with a clean checkout "
"process\n"
"with a minimal number of steps and a great useability on every page.\n"
"\n"
"Customize your checkout process to fit your business needs: payment modes,\n"
"delivery methods, cross-selling, special conditions, etc.\n"
"\n"
"And much more...\n"
"----------------\n"
"\n"
"### Online Sales\n"
"\n"
"-   Mobile Interface\n"
"-   Sell products, events or services\n"
"-   Flexible pricelists\n"
"-   Product multi-variants\n"
"-   Multiple stores\n"
"-   Great checkout process\n"
"\n"
"### Customer Service\n"
"\n"
"-   Customer Portal to track orders\n"
"-   Assisted shopping with website live chats\n"
"-   Returns management\n"
"-   Advanced shipping rules\n"
"-   Coupons or gift certificates\n"
"\n"
"### Order Management\n"
"\n"
"-   Advanced warehouse management features\n"
"-   Invoicing and accounting integration\n"
"-   Mass mailing and customer segmentations\n"
"-   Lead automation and marketing campaigns\n"
"-   Persistent shopping cart\n"
"\n"
"Fully Integrated With Other Apps\n"
"--------------------------------\n"
"\n"
"### CMS\n"
"\n"
"Easily create awesome websites with no technical knowledge required.\n"
"\n"
"### Blog\n"
"\n"
"Write news, attract new visitors, build customer loyalty.\n"
"\n"
"### Online Events\n"
"\n"
"Schedule, organize, promote or sell events online; conferences, webinars, "
"trainings, etc.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"Odoo e-Handel\n"
"---------------\n"
"\n"
"### Optimér dit salg med en effektiv onlinebutik.\n"
"\n"
"Odoo er en <a href=\"https://www.odoo.com/app/ecommerce\">open source-e-"
"handelsplatform</a>,\n"
"som du ikke har oplevet før. Få et brugervenligt produktkatalog\n"
"og detaljerede produktbeskrivelsessider.\n"
"\n"
"Det er fuldt udstyret, integreret med din administrationssoftware, helt\n"
"tilpasseligt og meget brugervenligt.\n"
"\n"
"Opret attraktive produktsider.\n"
"----------------------------\n"
"\n"
"Odoos entydige ›redigér inline‹ og metode baseret på designmoduler gør det\n"
"nemt at oprette produktsider. \"Vil du ændre prisen på et produkt, fremhæve "
"tekst eller tilføje et banner?\", bare klik og redigér.\n"
"Det, du ser, er det, du får. Virkelig.\n"
"\n"
"Træk og slip smukt designede *'designmoduler'* for at lave produktsider,\n"
"som dine kunder vil elske.\n"
"\n"
"Øg omsætningen pr. ordre.\n"
"-------------------------------\n"
"\n"
"Den indbyggede krydssalgsfunktion hjælper dig med at tilbyde relaterede "
"produkter til\n"
"det, kunden allerede har lagt i indkøbskurven, f.eks. tilbehør.\n"
"\n"
"Odoos mersalgsalgoritme giver dig mulighed for at vise besøgende lignende, "
"men\n"
"dyrere produkter med relevante incitamenter.\n"
"\n"
"Med funktionen til redigering i linjen kan du nemt ændre pris, lancere\n"
"kampagner eller finjustere produktbeskrivelser med et enkelt klik.\n"
"\n"
"Fuld integration med Google Analytics.\n"
"------------------------------------\n"
"\n"
"Få et klart overblik over din salgstragt. Odoos Google Analytics-trackere\n"
"er som standard konfigureret til at spore alle relevante begivenheder, såsom "
"indkøbskurve\n"
"og handlingsopfordringer.\n"
"\n"
"Da Odoos marketingværktøjer – som masseudsendelser og kampagner – også er "
"Google Analytics, får du et komplet overblik over din virksomhed.\n"
"\n"
"Strategisk målretning mod nye markeder.\n"
"------------------\n"
"\n"
"Få din hjemmeside oversat til flere sprog uden besvær. Odoo foreslår\n"
"oversættelser og anvender dem automatisk på tværs af siderne.\n"
"\n"
"Vores oversættelsesfunktion \"efter behov\" giver dig adgang til "
"professionelle\n"
"oversættere, som automatisk oversætter alle dine ændringer. Uanset om du "
"opdaterer\n"
"et blogindlæg, en side eller produktbeskrivelser,\n"
"bliver de oversatte versioner automatisk opdateret inden for ca. 32 timer.\n"
"\n"
"Finjustér dit katalog\n"
"----------------------\n"
"\n"
"Få fuld kontrol over, hvordan dine produkter præsenteres på katalogsiden:\n"
"reklameribboner, relaterede produktstørrelser, rabatter, varianter, gitter- "
"eller\n"
"listevisning m.m.\n"
"\n"
"Redigér ethvert produkt direkte inline, så din hjemmeside kan tilpasses dine "
"kunders behov.\n"
"\n"
"Tiltræk nye kunder\n"
"---------------------\n"
"\n"
"SEO-værktøjerne er klar til brug uden yderligere konfiguration. Odoo "
"foreslår\n"
"søgeord baseret på Googles mest søgte termer, Google Analytics sporer\n"
"indkøbskurvsbegivenheder, og sitemaps genereres automatisk til Google-"
"indeksering\n"
"m.m.\n"
"\n"
"Vi genererer automatisk struktureret indhold for at fremme dine produkter og "
"begivenheder\n"
"effektivt i Google.\n"
"\n"
"Udnyt sociale medier\n"
"---------------------\n"
"\n"
"Opret hurtigt nye landingssider med Odoos indbyggede redigeringsfunktion. "
"Send\n"
"besøgende fra dine marketingkampagner til specifikke sider for at\n"
"optimere konverteringer.\n"
"\n"
"Administrér dit forhandlernetværk.\n"
"-------------------------\n"
"\n"
"Administrér dit forhandlernetværk for at målrette nye markeder, styrke "
"lokal\n"
"tilstedeværelse eller udvide distributionen. Giv forhandlerne adgang til din "
"forhandlerportal for effektivt\n"
"samarbejde.\n"
"\n"
"Promovér dine forhandlere online, videresend leads til forhandlere (med "
"indbygget\n"
"geolokalisering), definér specifikke prislister og lancér et "
"loyalitetsprogram,\n"
"der giver særlige rabatter til dine bedste kunder eller forhandlere m.m.\n"
"\n"
"Udnyt Odoos fulde potentiale i din onlinebutik: kraftfuld skatteengine,\n"
"fleksible prisstrukturer, fuld lagerstyring, en\n"
"forhandlerportal, samt support til produkter med forskellige egenskaber – "
"fysiske varer,\n"
"begivenheder, tjenester, varianter og muligheder m.m.\n"
"\n"
"Du behøver ikke at forbinde til dit lager-, salgs- eller regnskabssystem.\n"
"Alt er fuldt integreret i Odoo – uden besvær og i realtid.\n"
"\n"
"En enkel og effektiv betalingsproces.\n"
"------------------------\n"
"\n"
"Konvertér de fleste besøgendes interesse til reelle ordrer med en enkel "
"betalingsproces,\n"
"få trin og høj brugervenlighed på alle sider.\n"
"\n"
"Tilpas betalingsprocessen efter dine forretningsbehov: betalingsformer,\n"
"leveringsmetoder, krydssalg, særlige betingelser m.m.\n"
"\n"
"Og så meget mere ...\n"
"----------------\n"
"\n"
"### Onlinesalg\n"
"\n"
"-   Mobilgrænseflade\n"
"-   Salg af produkter, events eller tjenester\n"
"-   Fleksible prislister\n"
"-   Produktvarianter\n"
"-   Flere butikker\n"
"-   Effektiv betalingsproces\n"
"\n"
"### Kundeservice\n"
"\n"
"-   Kundeportal til sporing af ordrer\n"
"-   Livechat på hjemmesiden til kundesupport\n"
"-   Returhåndtering\n"
"-   Avancerede forsendelsesregler\n"
"-   Kuponer og gavekort\n"
"\n"
"### Ordrehåndtering\n"
"\n"
"-   Avancerede lagerstyringsfunktioner\n"
"-   Integration af fakturering og regnskab\n"
"-   Massemail og kundesegmentering\n"
"-   Lead-automatisering og marketingkampagner\n"
"-   Vedvarende indkøbskurv\n"
"\n"
"Fuldt integreret med andre apps\n"
"--------------------------------\n"
"\n"
"### CMS\n"
"\n"
"Opret nemt professionelle hjemmesider uden teknisk viden.\n"
"\n"
"### Blog\n"
"\n"
"Skriv nyheder, tiltræk nye besøgende og styrk kundeloyalitet.\n"
"\n"
"### Onlinearrangementer\n"
"\n"
"Planlæg, organiser, promover og sælg begivenheder online – konferencer, "
"webinarer, kurser m.m.\n"
"\n"

